snippet.title: SENRAN KAGURA Burst Re: Newal - Yumi & Ice Queen Campaign DLC Trailer (PC/PS4)
snippet.description:
SENRAN KAGURA Burst Re: Newal - Yumi & Ice Queen Campaign DLC Trailer

Experience a brand new story over 10 missions with Yumi in the world of SENRAN KAGURA Burst Re:Newal. Yumi can also be used in all other missions within the game.
